<section class="grid gap-6 py-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
  <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-8 text-slate-900 shadow-xl shadow-slate-950/10">
    <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 uppercase">Recorder</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold">3 分だけ、今日を話す。</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
      書き切ろうとせず、今日の出来事や気持ちをそのまま声にしてください。
      3 分で自動停止するので、話しすぎる心配はいりません。
    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-8 rounded-[1.75rem] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6"
      data-controller="recorder"
      data-recorder-max-seconds-value="180"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Remaining</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-4xl font-semibold tabular-nums text-slate-950" data-recorder-target="timer">03:00</p>
        </div>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="inline-flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-950 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-white uppercase transition hover:bg-slate-800"
          data-recorder-target="recordButton"
          data-action="recorder#toggle"
        >
          Rec
        </button>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600" data-recorder-target="status">
        マイクへのアクセスを許可して、録音を始めてください。
      </p>

      <audio controls class="mt-5 hidden w-full" data-recorder-target="preview"></audio>

      <%= form_with model: @entry, class: "mt-6 space-y-4" do |form| %>
        <% if @entry.errors.any? %>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700">
            <%= @entry.errors.full_messages.to_sentence %>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <%= form.file_field :audio_file, accept: "audio/*", class: "block w-full text-sm text-slate-600 file:mr-4 file:rounded-full file:border-0 file:bg-slate-950 file:px-4 file:py-2 file:text-sm file:font-medium file:text-white", data: { recorder_target: "fileInput", action: "change->recorder#fileSelected" } %>
        <%= form.hidden_field :duration_seconds, value: 0, data: { recorder_target: "durationInput" } %>

        <%= form.submit "この録音を保存する", class: "inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-950 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:bg-slate-300", disabled: true, data: { recorder_target: "submitButton" } %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside class="rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/8 p-8 text-slate-100 backdrop-blur">
    <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400 uppercase">Prompt</p>
    <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">話すヒント</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
      <li>今日は何が一番心に残ったか</li>
      <li>うれしかったこと、引っかかったことは何か</li>
      <li>明日の自分に何を持ち越したいか</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/40 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        MVP ではまず録音保存までを安定させ、その次に
        Whisper 文字起こしと 1 行要約をつなげていく想定です。
      </p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>
